OL,3,CBusinesses share fears as Welsh
OL,4,Ccouncils put brakes on free parking
OL,6,FGwennan Campbell reports.
OL,8,FBusiness owners have shared their
OL,9,Ffears of trade dropping as a number of
OL,10,FWelsh councils look to put the brakes
OL,11,Fon free parking in a bid to save money.
OL,13,FMore than 3,500 people have signed a
OL,14,Fpetition against 's plans to scrap
OL,15,Ffree parking in residential shopping
OL,16,Fareas, while free parking has already
OL,17,Fbeen scrapped in Wrexham's council-
OL,18,Fowned car parks.
