OL,6,FCardiff Council said the proposed
OL,7,Fremoval of the gratuitous window -
OL,8,Fusually one or two hours - is one of
OL,9,Fthe "difficult decisions" it has had
OL,10,Fto make as it grapples with the "most
OL,11,Fchallenging" budget position it has
OL,12,Fever faced.
OL,14,FOne driver parked at a currently free
OL,15,Fcar park in Whitchurch said the
OL,16,Fpossible changes are "really
OL,17,Fdisappointing because the two hours
OL,18,Ffree parking is really useful just to
OL,19,Fdo everything you need to do here in
OL,20,Fthe village.
