OL,6,F"Two hours is just enough to do what
OL,7,Fyou need to do."
OL,9,FHe added he would not return if he had
OL,10,Fto pay for parking.
OL,12,FSpiro Gropetis, the owner of local
OL,13,Fchip shop Fintans, said: "If we lose
OL,14,Fthe parking in the village I am really
OL,15,Fworried that it will be the end of the
OL,16,Fvillage. If someone's coming in for
OL,17,Flunch and they're spending #3 to #4 on
OL,18,Flunch, if they've got to spend #3.50
OL,19,Fto park that lunch may no longer be
OL,20,Faffordable for them."
