OL,6,FHe added: "I think my biggest worry as
OL,7,Fwell is our competition. If people
OL,8,Fdon't use the village, you've got the
OL,9,Fsupermarkets. They have free parking
OL,10,Fup to three hours. Why is someone
OL,11,Fgoing to come into the village and pay
OL,12,Ffor their parking when they can go to
OL,13,Fthe supermarket and have it for free?"
OL,15,FAnother local said: "I don't disagree
OL,16,Fwith scrapping it, but I disagree with
OL,17,Fthe amount that they're charging.
