OL,6,FVisitors to council-owned car parks
OL,7,Fand on-street pay and display zones
OL,8,Fnear popular high streets - like those
OL,9,Fin Whitchurch, Llanishen, Rhiwbina,
OL,10,FCanton, Llandaff and Cardiff Bay -
OL,11,Fcould be be charged as soon as they
OL,12,Fpark.
OL,14,FUnmanaged car parking spaces on the
OL,15,Fpublic highways will not be affected
OL,16,Fby these changes.
OL,18,FWhen could these changes come into
OL,19,Feffect?
