OL,6,FWhether or not the change goes ahead
OL,7,Fis dependent on a Traffic Regulation
OL,8,FOrder (TRO) - a legal consultation
OL,9,Fprocess - which takes between six and
OL,10,Fnine months to complete.
OL,12,FTherefore free parking will remain in
OL,13,Fplace until at least October 2024.
OL,15,FCardiff Council said if this does go
OL,16,Fahead, visitors will have to start
OL,17,Fpaying this winter.
