OL,6,FCardiff council said the reasons why
OL,7,Ffree parking is being scrapped is down
OL,8,Fto a "challenging" budget and wanting
OL,9,Fto "encourage people to become less
OL,10,Freliant on their private car".
OL,12,FThey added, "any surplus income will
OL,13,Fbe re-invested into highway and
OL,14,Ftransport schemes, so we can continue
OL,15,Fto improve public transport, walking
OL,16,Fand cycling facilities across the city.
