OL,6,F"We are investing significantly in
OL,7,Fcycling and walking routes, as well as
OL,8,Fimproving the infrastructure for bus
OL,9,Ftravel, so bus operators can provide a
OL,10,Fbetter and more efficient service for
OL,11,Ftheir customers.
OL,13,F"By investing in public transport and
OL,14,Factive travel, we will provide a
OL,15,Fcredible alternative to travelling by
OL,16,Fprivate car, which in turn has
OL,17,Fsignificant benefits, giving residents
OL,18,Fand visitors better and healthier
OL,19,Foptions to travel around the city.
