OL,6,FAfter being introduced to support key
OL,7,Fworkers and city centre businesses
OL,8,Fboth during and after the coronavirus
OL,9,Fpandemic, senior councillors voted in
OL,10,Ffavour of axing free parking in the
OL,11,Fcity centre in April 2024 due to the
OL,12,Flocal authority facing a worsening
OL,13,Ffinancial landscape.
OL,15,FHarry owns a cafe in Wrexham city
OL,16,Fcentre. He said they used to be very
OL,17,Fbusy after 11 - which is when the free
OL,18,Fparking was allotted - and whilst they
OL,19,Fare still busy, he said there has been
OL,20,Fa "dip".
