OL,3,CBusinesses share fears as Welsh
OL,4,Ccouncils put brakes on free parking
OL,6,F"Definitely initially we've seen it's
OL,7,Fa lot quieter", he explained.
OL,9,F"Usually at 11am when it was free
OL,10,Fthere was an instant boom in customers
OL,11,Fand people coming into town. I didn't
OL,12,Fthink it would be so instant but yeah,
OL,13,Fit's definitely stopped being as busy
OL,14,Fstraight away."
OL,16,FHe said that he's heard a lot of
OL,17,Fpeople are "frustrated" with the
OL,18,Fchange.
