OL,6,F"There's people who come in everyday,
OL,7,Fespecially the retired, older
OL,8,Fgeneration. They come in everyday to
OL,9,Fget out and about - I suppose it's an
OL,10,Fextra cost for them so they probably
OL,11,Fstay at home a few more days a week."
OL,13,FHe said the city has been quieter
OL,14,Fsince the introduction of parking
OL,15,Fpayments, "definitely between the
OL,16,Fperiods in the afternoon, it's more
OL,17,Fquieter than it wasn't, I have seen
OL,18,Fthat initially.
